import React from 'react'
import MainComponent from '../frontend/Main/components'
import Head from 'next/head'
const Main = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Head>
        <title>Michsonrisa - Siempre un motivo para sonreir :)</title>
        <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1.0, width=device-width" />
      </Head>
      <MainComponent />
    </>
  )
}

export default Main
